# Commits: No Co-authored-by

## Rule

When creating or amending git commits in this project:

1. **Do NOT** add any `Co-authored-by:` line (or similar trailer) to commit messages.
2. **Do** use only the commit message text the user provides, with no extra trailers or signatures.

## Exception

Add a Co-authored-by line only if the user explicitly asks for it (e.g. "lägg till Co-authored-by" or "add co-author X").

## Why

The project owner does not want Co-authored-by or other attribution trailers in commits unless they specifically request it.
